      "title": "SSP Ruwan Gunasekara appointed Director Police Legal Division",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "SSP Ruwan Gunasekara has been appointed as the Director of the Police Legal Division by the Inspector General of Police.",
        "Police said SSP Gunasekara was appointed to the post with effect from August 22 on the approval of the Public Security Ministry Secretary.",
        "SSP Gunasekara who was also the former police spokesman was appointed to the post from the Director of the Judicial Protection Division."
      ],
